'''保罗·R·萨加德'''（{{lang-en|Paul Richard Thagard}}，1950年 – ）是一位[[加拿大|加拿大]][[哲学|哲学]]家，现为[[滑鐵盧大學|滑鐵盧大學]]教授，主要作品有《病因何在：科学家如何解释疾病》（''How Scientists Explain Disease''）、《心理学与认知科学哲学》（''Philosophy of Psycology and Cognitive Science''，与他人合著）等<ref name=GS>Google Scholar. https://scholar.google.ca/scholar?q=paul%20thagard&um=1&ie=UTF-8&sa=N&hl=en&tab=ws {{Wayback|url=https://scholar.google.ca/scholar?q=paul%20thagard&um=1&ie=UTF-8&sa=N&hl=en&tab=ws |date=20201012025557 }}</ref><ref name=CTA>Paul Thagard, ''Coherence in Thought and Action'' (Bradford Book, 2000, {{ISBN|0-262-20131-3}})</ref><ref name=PT>Paul Thagard, [https://www.psychologytoday.com/blog/hot-thought/201212/eleven-dogmas-analytic-philosophy "Eleven Dogmas of Analytic Philosophy"], 4 December 2012.</ref>。

